        <p class="tablespacerafter" />
        <p class="bodytext">To remove all text from the PIN Code and PIN Code Confirm text boxes, click <b><b>Clear</b></b>. To update the security settings, click <b><b>Apply</b></b>. </p>
        <p class="bodytext">
          <b>
            <b>Access Denied screen</b>
          </b>
        </p>
        <p class="bodytext">Two Access Denied screens might appear. One screen indicates you have tried to navigate into a screen you have no privileges to. The other screen indicates another user has navigated to a screen you have no privileges to.</p>
        <p class="bodytext">
          <b>
            <b>Resource Unavailable screen</b>
          </b>
        </p>
        <p class="bodytext">This screen appears when too many users are requesting the same screen at the same time or for other reasons the information does not appear. For more detailed information, see the system log.</p>
        <p class="bodytext">
          <b>Insight Display<b> screen access levels</b></b>
        </p>
        <p class="bodytext">Users must have user permissions for Onboard Administrator Bays to view the Insight Display screens. If a user does not have Onboard Administrator Bays permissions, an Access Denied screen appears.</p>
